# Environment Variables Configuration

## ML-Sharp API Configuration

After deploying to Hugging Face Spaces, update this file with your Space URL:

```env
# ML-Sharp 2D to 3D Conversion API
# Replace with your Hugging Face Space URL after deployment
VITE_MLSHARP_API_URL=https://YOUR-USERNAME-mlsharp-2d-to-3d.hf.space
```

## Example

If your Hugging Face username is `johndoe` and you named your Space `mlsharp-2d-to-3d`, your URL would be:

```env
VITE_MLSHARP_API_URL=https://johndoe-mlsharp-2d-to-3d.hf.space
```

## Old Colab Setup (Deprecated)

❌ **No longer needed** after Hugging Face deployment:
```env
# VITE_MLSHARP_API_URL=https://some-ngrok-url.ngrok-free.dev
```

The Hugging Face URL is **permanent** and never changes, unlike Ngrok URLs that change on every restart.
